                <h1>Change Your Instagram Story Background Easily</h1>
                <p>To change the background of your Instagram story, start by opening the app and tapping on the camera icon. Capture or upload a photo/video. Then, tap the brush icon at the top right, select a color, and use your finger to apply it as a background. Alternatively, you can use stickers, GIFs, or images to enhance the background!</p>
